### المرحلة 7 — DonorMedicalDocumentService + Repository (جديد)

#### [NEW] `IDonorMedicalDocumentRepository.cs` و `DonorMedicalDocumentRepository.cs`
في `BloodConnectAPI.DataAccess/Repositories/`

```csharp
interface IDonorMedicalDocumentRepository : IGenericRepository<DonorMedicalDocument>
{
    Task<IEnumerable<DonorMedicalDocument>> FindAsync(
        Expression<Func<DonorMedicalDocument, bool>> predicate);
}
```

#### [MODIFY] `IUnitOfWork.cs`
```diff
+ IDonorMedicalDocumentRepository DonorMedicalDocuments { get; }
```

#### [MODIFY] `UnitOfWork.cs`
```csharp
private IDonorMedicalDocumentRepository? _donorMedicalDocuments;
public IDonorMedicalDocumentRepository DonorMedicalDocuments =>
    _donorMedicalDocuments ??= new DonorMedicalDocumentRepository(_context);
```

#### [NEW] `IDonorMedicalDocumentService.cs`
```csharp
public interface IDonorMedicalDocumentService
{
    Task<ServiceResponse<DonorMedicalDocumentDto>> UploadDocumentAsync(
        SubmitMedicalDocumentDto dto, string uploadsRootPath, string uploadedByUserId);
    Task<ServiceResponse<DonorMedicalDocumentDto>> GetByIdAsync(int documentId);
    Task<ServiceResponse<IEnumerable<DonorMedicalDocumentDto>>> GetByDonorIdAsync(int donorId);
    Task<ServiceResponse<DonorMedicalDocumentDto>> VerifyDocumentAsync(
        int documentId, VerifyMedicalDocumentDto dto, string verifiedByUserId);
    Task<ServiceResponse<bool>> DeleteAsync(int documentId, string uploadsRootPath);
}
```

#### [NEW] `DonorMedicalDocumentService.cs`

**`UploadDocumentAsync`:**
```
1. التحقق من وجود المتبرع
2. التحقق من أن الملف غير فارغ
3. التحقق من الامتداد (.pdf, .jpg, .jpeg, .png فقط)
4. إنشاء المجلد: wwwroot/uploads/medical-documents/
5. اسم فريد: {DonorID}_{DocumentType}_{Guid}{ext}
6. حفظ الملف بـ CopyToAsync
7. المسار النسبي: /uploads/medical-documents/{fileName}
8. إنشاء DonorMedicalDocument وحفظه
9. إذا donor.ApprovalStatus == PendingDocuments → تحديثها إلى PendingApproval
10. SaveChangesAsync
```

**`VerifyDocumentAsync`:**
```csharp
document.IsVerified = dto.IsVerified;
document.Notes = dto.Notes;
```

**`DeleteAsync`:**
```csharp
var absolutePath = Path.Combine(uploadsRootPath, document.FilePath.TrimStart('/'));
absolutePath = absolutePath.Replace("/", "\\");  // Windows path fix
if (File.Exists(absolutePath)) File.Delete(absolutePath);
```

#### [NEW] مجلد `wwwroot/uploads/medical-documents/`
أُنشئ مجلد التحميل في مشروع `BloodConnectAPI` مع ملف `.gitkeep`.

